(20, 'FULL DAY TOUR OF YAZD', 44, 37, 40, '8 hrs', 'Old town of YAZD,  Eskandar Jail, Old & Traditional Bazaar, Doulatabad Garden', '<p><span class=\"metin\">After breakfast proceed to Silence tower in Safaeiyeh area place which were used to placing corps for vultures to eat but from 80 years ago it not continued but buried in cemetery so now just the place remain to visit. Visit fire temple of Yazd with sacred alive fire belong to Zoroastrian followers in Yazd. Visit Mirchaghmak complex included Hoseyniyeh , Mosque , Bazar &amp; Square this monument is belong to 400 years ago Safavid &nbsp;governing time. Visit Jame Mosque of Yazd which has highest Minarets among mosque of Iran, collection of different dynasty architectures from TAYMORID governing time 900 years ago till Gajarid governing time 200 years old.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><span class=\"metin\"><strong>Available Guiding Language(s):</strong> <br />&bull; Local tour guide (Monolingual)<br />&bull; English, Persian <br /><br /><strong>Included Services:</strong><br />&bull; All sightseeing mentioned in the itinerary &nbsp;<br />&bull;&nbsp;Private guiding and driving service<br />&bull; Pick up from and drop off to city center hotels <br /><br /><strong>Excluded Services:</strong><br />&bull; Tips to the guide and driver (optional)<br />&bull; Meals / beverage<br />&bull; Personal expenses</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><span class=\"metin\">&bull;&nbsp;This tour operates with minimum <strong>2</strong> pax booking.<br />&bull; In the rare event of lack of availability due to special events an alternative day or service may be advised.<br />&bull; Amendments are upon availability and may require supplement fee.<br />&bull;&nbsp;Full cancellation applies in the event of No-Show.<br />&bull; Hotel pickups from outside of city center is upon availability and may require supplement fee. </span></p>\r\n<hr size=\"1\" />\r\n<p><span class=\"metin\">Tax:&nbsp;Included<br /></span></p>\r\n<hr size=\"1\"