(28, 'KISH DOLPHIN SHOW AND BIRDS GARDEN TOUR', 41, 37, 40, '4 hours', 'DOLPHIN SHOW AND BIRDS GARDEN', '<p><span style=\"font-family: DefaultFont;\">Driver picks you up at your hotel. You will visit Birds Garden. After that you will see Salt Water Aquarium and enjoy this beautiful and colorful sight that displays marine species unique to the Persian Gulf. Next stop is The Dolphin Park which is very amusing and exciting. The Dolphin Park is the unique ocean atrium in the Middle East, and visitors can enjoy spectacular dolphin and other sea mammal shows in a family-oriented atmosphere. The Dolphin Park is a park located at the south east corner of Kish Island. It is surrounded by over 22,000 palm trees, and includes a dolphinarium, butterfly garden, silkworm compound, bird garden, artificial rain forest, volcanic mountain, orchid garden, and cactus garden. The dolphinarium includes the largest man made pool on the island, and exhibits dolphins, sea lions, and white whales. Driver drops you off at your hotel in the end.</span></p>', '<p><span class=\"metin\"><strong>Available Guiding Language(s):</strong> <br />&bull; Local tour guide (Monolingual)<br />&bull; English, Persian <br /><br /><strong>Included Services:</strong><br />&bull; All sightseeing mentioned in the itinerary &nbsp;<br />&bull; Pick up from and drop off to city center hotels<br />&bull; Land transportation by air-conditioned non-smoking vehicle <br /><br /><strong>Excluded Services:</strong><br />&bull; Tips to the guide and driver (optional)<br />&bull; Beverage with meals<br />&bull; Meals / beverage<br />&bull; Personal expenses</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><span class=\"metin\">&bull;&nbsp;This tour operates with minimum <strong>2</strong> booking.<br />&bull; In the rare event of lack of availability due to special events an alternative day or service may be advised.<br />&bull; Amendments are upon availability and may require supplement fee.<br />&bull;&nbsp;Full cancellation applies in t