(29, 'KISH HISTORICAL SITES TOUR', 0, 0, 0, '', 'Green Tree/Harireh & Kariz Historical city', '<p><span class=\"metin\">With its luxury cars and hotels, Kish is an island of extravagance where one can pamper themselves for a few days, forget their worries, go on shopping sprees and immerse themselves in the warm blue waters of the Persian Gulf. Famed for its coral reefs, Kish is a flat island with no mountains or any other natural elevations. It is also one of the Persian Gulf islands with the longest sunny hours, ideal for people who love to doze in the sun and wake up with a natural tan.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><span class=\"metin\"><strong>Available Guiding Language(s):</strong> <br />&bull; Local tour guide (Monolingual)<br />&bull; English, Persian <br /><br /><strong>Included Services:</strong><br />&bull; All sightseeing mentioned in the itinerary &nbsp;<br />&bull; Pick up from and drop off to city center hotels <br /><br /><strong>Excluded Services:</strong><br />&bull; Tips to the guide and driver (optional)<br />&bull; Meals / beverage<br />&bull; Personal expenses</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><span class=\"metin\">&bull;&nbsp;This tour operates with minimum <strong>2 </strong>booking.<br />&bull; In the rare event of lack of availability due to special events an alternative day or service may be advised.<br />&bull; Amendments are upon availability and may require supplement fee.<br />&bull;&nbsp;Full cancellation applies in the event of No-Show.<br />&bull; Hotel pickups from outside of city center is upon availability and may require supplement fee. </span></p>\r\n<hr size=\"1\" />\r\n<p><span class=\"metin\">Tax:&nbsp;Included <br /></span></p>\r\n<hr size=\"1\" />\r\n<p><span class=\"metin\">Cancellation Policy: This service can be cancelled without any penalties&nbsp;<strong>5</strong>&nbsp;day(s) prior to first service date. </span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><span class=\"metin\"><strong>Departure Time:</strong><br />9:00 am<br />!H